Package: spatialcompare
Type: Package
Title: Comparative Tables of Spatial Features Preserving Accurate Spatial Dimensions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Toby Wilkincon
Maintainer: Toby Wilkinson <open@tobywilkinson.co.uk>
Description: This package designed to facilitate the construction of infographics which place spatial features side-by-side.
   The package aims to preserve the accurate spatial dimensions of the features while translating their spatial position to allow visual comparison. 
   Applications include visual comparison the dimensions of modern or ancient cities, study regions or building sizes in two dimensional space. 
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
